modName: Collection of outfits from Black Desert - DELETED
summary: This is a collection of 10 mods: outfits from BDO. Body CBBE. + support for Bodyslide.
descriptionHtml:
Outfits from BDO. Body CBBE. + support for Bodyslide.

This is the merger of 10 of my mods associated with BDO for women:

1.  BDO_Ran_Phalaenopsis_ v2.1 (CBBE)
2.  BDO_Sorc_Cartian 1.1
3.  BDO_Kun_Night_Cat v1.0 
4.  BDO DK_PuffMini (Female)
5.  BDO_Valkyrie_ v1.21 (female CBBE)
6.  BDO_Witch_ v1.0 (female)
7.  Dark_Knight_BDO v1.5+ HDT Weapons (female)
8.  Pirate_Corsair_BDOv1.0 (femalee)
9.  BDO Milren_Fedora (Female) - 1.1
10.  Robes of the Witch HDT (Chaphel & Dint) v1.1

All elements of the armor can be enchanted and improved. To create - use the forge or mod AddItem Menu.

In the download section is an ESP-file translated into English. First you need to download the mod itself, the link below.

[color=#ffd966][i][u][size=4]What you need to do to get everything working:[/size][/u][/i][/color]

1. Find me on the site ([url=https://gamer-mods.ru/index/8]click on me[/url]). [u][b][size=2]You need to register on the site to download any mod.[/size][/b][/u]  
2. In the "Files" section, find the mod-pack "" "[b][color=#f1c232]Сборник нарядов из BDO от dint999[/color][/b]" and download it.
3. Download the English .eps file and replace the original Rus-esp.

[color=#ffff00][size=2]Requirements: [/size][/color]

- Skyrim 1.9.32.0.8
- Heels Sound 1.3 and higher 
- HDT HighHeels System
- CBBE body with physics
- RaceMenu
- HDT Physics Extension
- SKSE (for physics work)
- the skeleton XPMSE

[i][u][color=#cc0000][size=5][center]Credits[/center][/size][/color][/u][/i]1. Bethesda Game Studios
2. PearlAbyss
3. 3Ds Max
4. Havok
5. Dsion 
6. IceKK 
7. Chaphel
